{"tid":1214391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HKUSPACE 校長對6月12號行動之表態","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:39:45.000Z","uid":146656,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4c0ecc29d97c9a012525d97ae490023e9c0246","tid":1214391,"uid":146656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:14:24.000Z","msg":"啱啱出左封email， 冇割蓆反而承認政府錯失！果日都有開海富campus比我地休息，以下係封信：<br />\n<br />\nDear Students, <br />\n<br />\nIt has been saddening to see our beloved city overwhelmed by chaos, with rubber bullets and tear gas fired at students and young people. <br />\n<br />\nThe management team of HKUSPACE Community College is deeply concerned about the worsening situation in Admiralty triggered by the protest against the extradition law proposed by Government. We are particularly concerned about the safety and well-being of our students who may be taking part in the protest. <br />\n<br />\nI understand that when a government fails its people, people may think they have the rights to resort to rigorous means to ensure their voices are heard. For those of you taking part in the protest, while I appreciate your sincerity and respect the path of action you have chosen to take, please also be aware of the possible consequences that may result. Most important of all, I would urge you to be mindful of your personal safety at all times. <br />\n<br />\nLS Chan <br />\n*** <br />\nLS Chan, Prof <br />\nCollege Principal<br />\nHKUSPACE Community College<br />\nHong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qro9UkR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQro9UkR.png&h=d7667fcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"beeb2ac3ce7044f4df98fe093aeedc81b40d77f3","tid":1214391,"uid":146656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a38d0eea5da2dd7b166d986d9589202a522671c","tid":1214391,"uid":146656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d0db065ce4899c702737a06a42220804686cf282","tid":1214391,"uid":227376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d8212a377948664e475586160b0436f8b83d94d","tid":1214391,"uid":200580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7cb43ada9e3f9d95aa824c89fd03834ca465bcdc","tid":1214391,"uid":256908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"真港大"},{"pid":"1d039d3990876b2fc2ca342e89a44d76acb67ad0","tid":1214391,"uid":118537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19ba9cf32685fb9c63e427a16d3f5b8e6719a48a","tid":1214391,"uid":35830,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"一句講曬，就係唔不反對，仲有保重。"},{"pid":"8c33746654e64a54c27870b77d6e9de6868e8a46","tid":1214391,"uid":146656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"18fd5bfce6c80ae0fba48ed72a1292a1a7215e71","tid":1214391,"uid":146656,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1d039d3990876b2fc2ca342e89a44d76acb67ad0","tid":1214391,"uid":118537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"唔係港人校長啊，係HKUSPACE校長"},{"pid":"d623951c469fd79083ab0586f1ed48bd61d5ad67","tid":1214391,"uid":146656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18fd5bfce6c80ae0fba48ed72a1292a1a7215e71","tid":1214391,"uid":146656,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1d039d3990876b2fc2ca342e89a44d76acb67ad0","tid":1214391,"uid":118537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"唔係港人校長啊，係HKUSPACE校長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:29:3